OL,3,CConcert hall's roof leaks just months
OL,4,Cafter #132m renovation
OL,6,FA concert hall that cost Bristol City
OL,7,FCouncil #132 million to rebuild has a
OL,8,Fleaky roof less than eight months
OL,9,Fafter it reopened.
OL,11,FPeople attending a performance on
OL,12,FFriday 5 July said they noticed water
OL,13,Fdripping from the foyer ceiling at the
OL,14,FBristol Beacon.
OL,16,FThe renovation work included restoring
OL,17,Fthe old entrance foyer area with new
OL,18,Fstaircases around the original
OL,19,FVictorian architecture.
