OL,6,FIt was on the mezzanine level that Jen
OL,7,FSmith and her friends saw the roof
OL,8,Fleaking after heavy rain.
OL,10,FJen said: "In the interval, a friend
OL,11,Fsat down on a seat outside of the
OL,12,Fauditorium, I noticed something flash
OL,13,Fby her and realised there was water
OL,14,Fcoming through the ceiling.
OL,16,F"I think the Beacon knew it was
OL,17,Fleaking because there was a table and
OL,18,Ftwo chairs perfectly positioned either
OL,19,Fside of where the water was coming in.
