OL,6,F"It looked like it was an attempt to
OL,7,Fdisguise it. My friend went over to
OL,8,Falert a member of the front-of-house
OL,9,Fteam.
OL,11,F"I started filming it because it's
OL,12,Fwild isn't it? All that money, open
OL,13,F(eight) months and water is coming in
OL,14,Fthe roof.
OL,16,F"You expect it from old theatres, but
OL,17,Fnot a newly refurbished top-of-the-
OL,18,Frange concert hall that's just had
OL,19,F#132 million spent on it," she added.
