OL,6,FBosses at the venue said the leak was
OL,7,Fsmall and did not last very long. They
OL,8,Fadded work to fix it was started
OL,9,Fimmediately.
OL,11,FSarah Robertson, director of
OL,12,Fcommunications at Bristol Beacon:
OL,13,F"After a period of heavy rain on
OL,14,FFriday night, there was a minor leak
OL,15,Fin the flat roof above the Lantern
OL,16,Ffoyer.
OL,18,F"Our teams responded promptly to the
OL,19,Fissue and it is being fixed.
